      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@\n+created: 2026-01-08\n+title: Enhanced Documentation and Schema Updates\n+intro: >-\n+  This release improves OCSF documentation synchronization with content-based change\n+  detection and transitions to pre-committed schema references. The guide agent now\n+  uses Claude Sonnet for enhanced reasoning on complex schema questions."
    },
